cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper deals with semantic segmentation of high-resolution aerial images using a novel scale-aware module. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new module that can be embedded in existing networks, which suggests that it may fall under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of aerial images also suggests that it may belong to cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.RO (Robotics).
